==English==
===Noun===
'''[[star]] [[macromolecule]]'''
#{{chemistry}} a macromolecule having a single [[branch point]] from which [[linear]] [[chain]]s (or [[arm]]s) [[emanate]]
===Usage notes===
* They are named according to the number of arms e.g. "five-star macromolecule"
===Derived terms===
*[[regular star macromolecule]]
*[[variegated star macromolecule]]